headline: NTT DATA and CrowdStrike Expand Partnership to Strengthen AI-Powered Cyber Resilience
summary: TOKYO & AUSTIN, Texas, March 17, 2025--NTT DATA, a global digital business and IT services leader, and CrowdStrike, a global cybersecurity leader, today announced an expanded partnership to power NTT DATA's managed cybersecurity services with the AI-native CrowdStrike Falcon® cybersecurity platform.
